author: woonsan
msg: JS2-949: Adds javascript codes to add contributed head elements.
Note that if a contributed head element has ID attribute, then the desktop javascript would add the element only once.
Otherwise, the desktop script will add the contributed head element every time when a portlet is rendered.
Now, I'd like to move to portlet migrations.

author: jukka
msg: JCRRMI-13: Enhancement to get RMI through firewalls
Added a port number attribute to RemoteAdapterFactory interface. This port (0 for a random port) is used by all ServerObject instances created by that factory.
The attribute is initialized to the value of the org.apache.jackrabbit.rmi.port system property, or to 0 if the property is not set.
Thanks to Tony Richardson for the idea!
